To those with the : AFTER EFFECTS ERROR: opening resource file "twitch.aex" - unexpected end-of-file (-39).
(3 :: 54)

error. That is because this is the PC version of Twitch. The Mac versions will have a .plugin extension, NOT aex. You will have to go looking elsewhere for it. Try googling 'Twitch 1.1 for Mac' that should find it for you fast.
